title: Google Cloud Platform: A Tour into recent features and What to expect from Google Cloud Next
description: Google Cloud Platform has seen significant momentum in the last year with key platform differentiators and a growing customer base. This talk takes you through a whirlwind tour of key GCP differentiators and some key features that have been released over the last several months.

title: Only with Apps Script
description: With most businesses adapting G Suite to collaborate and optimize their workflows, there's an opportunity for makers to use it's low-code developer platform and leverage its capabilities to build things that can only be done using the Apps Script ecosystem viz. Add-ons & Data Studio Community Connectors.

title: Reimagine Work with AI/ ML, Chatbots, & Connected Systems over G Suite
description: This talk will enable businessmen to do "EVERYTHING" on G Suite, Google's Productivity, and Collaboration Suite. A complete Google Solution can lead to up to 2/3rd savings on Technology and up to 10X increase in productivity for organizations. In this talk, we shall focus on AI/ML facilities in G Suite, Chat Rooms, and Chatbots on Google Chat and how you can truly transform work by connecting your ERP/ CRM with G Suite and live and breath completely on Cloud.

title: What's new in Google Compute Engine
description: Google Compute Engine is an infrastructure service provided as part of the Google Cloud Platform. It is available at several Google data centers worldwide and is provided exclusively on an on-demand basis.
